---
/**
 * Storytelling visual — 5 cenas do produto.
 * "Da mensagem ao caixa": lead chega → IA responde → time fecha →
 *                          time inteiro num número → dados que viram decisão.
 *
 * Cada cena alterna lado (mockup esq/dir) pra ritmo visual.
 * Scroll-driven cinema: cena 1 estática (âncora), cenas 2-5 fazem
 *                       fade+scale crescendo ao entrar e recuando ao sair.
 */
---

<section id="produto" class="relative bg-slate-50 py-24 lg:py-32 overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Decorativo: blob azul muito sutil no canto -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[28rem] h-[28rem] bg-primary-100 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-30 pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 relative">

    <!-- Header da seção -->
    <div data-reveal class="max-w-2xl mb-20">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-primary-600 mb-4">
        Como funciona
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight leading-[1.05]">
        Da mensagem<br />ao caixa.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mt-6 leading-relaxed">
        Lead chega, IA responde, time fecha. Tudo no mesmo lugar, e você acompanha cada passo.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
         CENA 1 — Lead chega (mockup ESQUERDA, texto DIREITA)
         Cena 1 é ESTÁTICA: sempre visível, sem transform no scroll.
    ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <div data-cena class="lg:min-h-[70vh] py-8 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">
      <!-- Mockup: inbox -->
      <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-200/40 to-transparent rounded-3xl blur-2xl"></div>
          <div class="relative bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl shadow-slate-900/10 border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden">
            <!-- Mac window bar -->
            <div class="bg-slate-50 border-b border-slate-200 px-3 py-2.5 flex items-center gap-1.5">
              <span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-rose-400"></span>
              <span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-amber-400"></span>
              <span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-400"></span>
              <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 ml-3 font-medium">app.kora.com.br · Inbox</span>
            </div>

            <!-- Inbox header -->
            <div class="px-4 pt-4 pb-3 border-b border-slate-100">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">Caixa de entrada</p>
                <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-medium">3 novos</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 mt-2.5">
                <span class="text-[10px] font-semibold px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-primary-50 text-primary-700 border border-primary-100">Todos</span>
                <span class="text-[10px] font-medium px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-slate-500">Anúncios</span>
                <span class="text-[10px] font-medium px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-slate-500">Orgânico</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Conversation rows -->
            <div class="divide-y divide-slate-100">
              <!-- Row 1: Facebook Ads -->
              <div class="px-4 py-3 flex items-start gap-3 bg-primary-50/40">
                <div class="size-9 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-rose-400 to-pink-500 flex items-center justify-center text-white text-xs font-bold shrink-0">M</div>
                <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2">
                    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 truncate">Maria Silva</p>
                    <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 shrink-0">agora</span>
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-xs text-slate-600 truncate mt-0.5">Vi o anúncio de vocês, queria saber se ainda tem...</p>
                  <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-[9px] font-semibold mt-1.5 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded bg-[#1877F2]/10 text-[#1877F2]">
                    <svg width="8" height="8" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M24 12.073c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12s-12 5.373-12 12c0 5.99 4.388 10.954 10.125 11.854v-8.385H7.078v-3.47h3.047V9.43c0-3.007 1.792-4.669 4.533-4.669 1.312 0 2.686.235 2.686.235v2.953H15.83c-1.491 0-1.956.925-1.956 1.874v2.25h3.328l-.532 3.47h-2.796v8.385C19.612 23.027 24 18.062 24 12.073z"/></svg>
                    Anúncio Facebook
                  </span>
                </div>
                <span class="size-2 rounded-full bg-primary-600 shrink-0 mt-1.5 animate-[pulseSoft_2s_ease-in-out_infinite]"></span>
              </div>

              <!-- Row 2: Instagram -->
              <div class="px-4 py-3 flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="size-9 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-400 to-orange-500 flex items-center justify-center text-white text-xs font-bold shrink-0">J</div>
                <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2">
                    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 truncate">João Costa</p>
                    <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 shrink-0">2 min</span>
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-xs text-slate-600 truncate mt-0.5">Olá, vi seu post no Instagram. Vocês entregam pra Curitiba?</p>
                  <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-[9px] font-semibold mt-1.5 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded bg-pink-50 text-pink-700">
                    <svg width="8" height="8" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2.163c3.204 0 3.584.012 4.85.07 3.252.148 4.771 1.691 4.919 4.919.058 1.265.069 1.645.069 4.849 0 3.205-.012 3.584-.069 4.849-.149 3.225-1.664 4.771-4.919 4.919-1.266.058-1.644.07-4.85.07-3.204 0-3.584-.012-4.849-.07-3.26-.149-4.771-1.699-4.919-4.92-.058-1.265-.07-1.644-.07-4.849 0-3.204.013-3.583.07-4.849.149-3.227 1.664-4.771 4.919-4.919 1.266-.057 1.645-.069 4.849-.069zM12 0C8.741 0 8.333.014 7.053.072 2.695.272.273 2.69.073 7.052.014 8.333 0 8.741 0 12c0 3.259.014 3.668.072 4.948.2 4.358 2.618 6.78 6.98 6.98C8.333 23.986 8.741 24 12 24c3.259 0 3.668-.014 4.948-.072 4.354-.2 6.782-2.618 6.979-6.98.059-1.28.073-1.689.073-4.948 0-3.259-.014-3.667-.072-4.947-.196-4.354-2.617-6.78-6.979-6.98C15.668.014 15.259 0 12 0zm0 5.838a6.162 6.162 0 100 12.324 6.162 6.162 0 000-12.324zM12 16a4 4 0 110-8 4 4 0 010 8zm6.406-11.845a1.44 1.44 0 100 2.881 1.44 1.44 0 000-2.881z"/></svg>
                    Instagram
                  </span>
                </div>
                <span class="size-2 rounded-full bg-primary-600 shrink-0 mt-1.5"></span>
              </div>

              <!-- Row 3: Orgânico -->
              <div class="px-4 py-3 flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="size-9 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-400 to-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center text-white text-xs font-bold shrink-0">C</div>
                <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2">
                    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 truncate">Carla Lima</p>
                    <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 shrink-0">5 min</span>
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-xs text-slate-600 truncate mt-0.5">Boa tarde! Recebi indicação da Patrícia, vocês podem...</p>
                  <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-[9px] font-semibold mt-1.5 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded bg-slate-100 text-slate-600">
                    <svg width="8" height="8" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M20 4H4c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v12c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h16c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V6c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 4l-8 5-8-5V6l8 5 8-5v2z"/></svg>
                    Indicação
                  </span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Cursor flutuante + tooltip (FORA do frame pra não ser cortado pelo overflow-hidden) -->
          <div
            class="absolute z-30 pointer-events-none"
            style="top: 138px; left: 58%; animation: cursorBounce 2.4s ease-in-out infinite;"
          >
            <span class="absolute -top-1 -left-1 size-8 rounded-full bg-primary-400/20 animate-[pulseSoft_2s_ease-in-out_infinite]"></span>
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="drop-shadow-md relative">
              <path d="M5 3l6 16 2.5-6.5L20 10 5 3z" fill="white" stroke="#0f172a" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
            <div class="absolute top-7 left-5 bg-slate-900 text-white text-[10px] font-medium rounded-md px-2 py-1 whitespace-nowrap shadow-lg">
              Anúncio: Vestido Floral · R$ 89,90
              <div class="absolute -top-1 left-3 size-2 bg-slate-900 rotate-45"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Texto cena 1 -->
      <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center size-10 rounded-xl bg-primary-100 text-primary-700 font-bold text-lg mb-4">1</span>
        <h3 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight leading-[1.1]">
          O lead chega e você<br />
          <span class="text-primary-600">já sabe de onde.</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mt-5 leading-relaxed max-w-md">
          Anúncio do Facebook, post do Instagram, indicação por boca-a-boca.
          Todo lead cai num inbox único, etiquetado pela origem. Você sabe exatamente
          o que está dando ROI.
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-6 space-y-2.5 text-sm text-slate-700">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" class="text-primary-600 shrink-0"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            Click-to-WhatsApp Ads do Meta rastreado automático
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" class="text-primary-600 shrink-0"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            Conversas do site, Instagram e Facebook no mesmo inbox
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" class="text-primary-600 shrink-0"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            Relatório por campanha, anúncio e palavra-chave
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
         CENA 2 — IA responde (mockup DIREITA, texto ESQUERDA)
         Entra de baixo crescendo, sai pra cima recuando.
    ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <div data-cena class="lg:min-h-[70vh] py-8 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">
      <!-- Texto cena 2 -->
      <div>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center size-10 rounded-xl bg-primary-100 text-primary-700 font-bold text-lg mb-4">2</span>
        <h3 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight leading-[1.1]">
          A IA atende em segundos,<br />
          <span class="text-primary-600">qualquer hora.</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mt-5 leading-relaxed max-w-md">
          22h, domingo, feriado. A IA responde, qualifica perguntando o que importa,
          e libera as conversas quentes pro seu time. O cliente nunca espera;
          você nunca perde a janela.
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-6 space-y-2.5 text-sm text-slate-700">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" class="text-primary-600 shrink-0"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            Treina com o tom de voz da sua empresa
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" class="text-primary-600 shrink-0"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            Passa pra humano no momento certo
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" class="text-primary-600 shrink-0"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            Manda áudio, imagem e link igual gente
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Mockup: chat snippet com IA -->
      <div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-gradient-to-bl from-primary-200/40 to-transparent rounded-3xl blur-2xl"></div>
          <div class="relative bg-[#E5DDD5] rounded-2xl p-5 shadow-xl shadow-slate-900/15 border border-slate-200/50">
            <div class="space-y-2.5">
              <div class="flex justify-start">
                <div class="max-w-[80%] bg-white rounded-2xl rounded-tl-md px-3.5 py-2 shadow-sm">
                  <p class="text-sm text-slate-800">Boa noite! É possível agendar pra amanhã às 14h?</p>
                  <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 text-right mt-1">22:47</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-2 py-1">
                <div class="size-5 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-700 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 relative">
                  <svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white" style="animation: sparkle 1.6s ease-in-out infinite;">
                    <path d="M12 2L13.5 8.5L20 10L13.5 11.5L12 18L10.5 11.5L4 10L10.5 8.5L12 2Z"/>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="absolute -top-0.5 -right-0.5 size-1 bg-primary-300 rounded-full" style="animation: sparkle 1.6s ease-in-out 0.3s infinite;"></span>
                  <span class="absolute -bottom-0.5 -left-0.5 size-1 bg-primary-300 rounded-full" style="animation: sparkle 1.6s ease-in-out 0.7s infinite;"></span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-[11px] font-semibold text-primary-700">Kora IA pensando...</p>
                <span class="inline-flex gap-0.5 ml-1">
                  <span class="size-1 bg-primary-400 rounded-full" style="animation: pulseSoft 1s ease-in-out infinite;"></span>
                  <span class="size-1 bg-primary-400 rounded-full" style="animation: pulseSoft 1s ease-in-out 0.2s infinite;"></span>
                  <span class="size-1 bg-primary-400 rounded-full" style="animation: pulseSoft 1s ease-in-out 0.4s infinite;"></span>
                </span>
              </div>

              <div class="flex justify-end">
                <div class="max-w-[85%] bg-[#DCF8C6] rounded-2xl rounded-tr-md px-3.5 py-2 shadow-sm">
                  <p class="text-[10px] font-semibold text-primary-700 mb-1 flex items-center gap-1">
                    <svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v2h4a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v10a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h4V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2Z"/></svg>
                    Atendente IA
                  </p>
                  <p class="text-sm text-slate-800">Boa noite! Tenho horário às 14h amanhã sim 💙 Posso confirmar pra você?</p>
                  <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 text-right mt-1">22:47 ✓✓</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-4 flex items-center gap-2 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-full px-3 py-1.5 w-max mx-auto shadow-sm">
              <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="text-amber-500"><path d="M13 2L3 14h7v8l10-12h-7V2z"/></svg>
              <span class="text-[11px] font-semibold text-slate-700 tabular-nums">Respondeu em 3s · 22h47 de domingo</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
         CENA 3 — Time fecha (mockup ESQUERDA, texto DIREITA)
         Kanban maior + card sendo arrastado + drop zone visível.
    ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <div data-cena class="lg:min-h-[70vh] py-8 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">
      <!-- Mockup: kanban maior com drag visual -->
      <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-gradient-to-tr from-emerald-200/40 to-transparent rounded-3xl blur-2xl"></div>
          <div class="relative bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl shadow-slate-900/10 border border-slate-200 overflow-visible">
            <!-- Mac window bar -->
            <div class="bg-slate-50 border-b border-slate-200 px-3 py-2.5 flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-t-2xl">
              <span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-rose-400"></span>
              <span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-amber-400"></span>
              <span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-400"></span>
              <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 ml-3 font-medium">app.kora.com.br · Funil</span>
            </div>

            <!-- Kanban -->
            <div class="p-4 bg-slate-50/50 relative rounded-b-2xl">
              <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-3">

                <!-- Coluna 1: Triagem -->
                <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-slate-200 p-2.5">
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2.5">
                    <p class="text-[11px] font-semibold text-slate-700">Triagem</p>
                    <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 tabular-nums">3</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="space-y-1.5">
                    <div class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded p-2">
                      <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 mb-1">
                        <div class="size-4 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-rose-400 to-pink-500 text-white text-[8px] font-bold flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">P</div>
                        <p class="text-[10px] font-semibold text-slate-800 truncate">Pedro N.</p>
                      </div>
                      <p class="text-[9px] text-slate-500 truncate">orçamento</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded p-2">
                      <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 mb-1">
                        <div class="size-4 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-400 to-blue-500 text-white text-[8px] font-bold flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">A</div>
                        <p class="text-[10px] font-semibold text-slate-800 truncate">Ana B.</p>
                      </div>
                      <p class="text-[9px] text-slate-500 truncate">consulta</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded p-2">
                      <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 mb-1">
                        <div class="size-4 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-400 to-orange-500 text-white text-[8px] font-bold flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">R</div>
                        <p class="text-[10px] font-semibold text-slate-800 truncate">Rafael S.</p>
                      </div>
                      <p class="text-[9px] text-slate-500 truncate">primeiro contato</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Coluna 2: Negociação (origem do drag — placeholder dashed) -->
                <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-slate-200 p-2.5">
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2.5">
                    <p class="text-[11px] font-semibold text-slate-700">Negociação</p>
                    <span class="text-[10px] text-amber-700 font-bold tabular-nums">R$ 2,1k</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="space-y-1.5">
                    <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded p-2">
                      <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 mb-1">
                        <div class="size-4 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-rose-400 to-pink-500 text-white text-[8px] font-bold flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">M</div>
                        <p class="text-[10px] font-semibold text-slate-800 truncate">Maria S.</p>
                      </div>
                      <p class="text-[9px] text-amber-700 font-bold truncate">R$ 1.290</p>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Placeholder dashed: onde o card arrastado estava -->
                    <div class="border-2 border-dashed border-slate-300 rounded p-2 bg-slate-50/30">
                      <p class="text-[9px] text-slate-400 text-center italic">arrastando...</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded p-2">
                      <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 mb-1">
                        <div class="size-4 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-400 to-purple-500 text-white text-[8px] font-bold flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">L</div>
                        <p class="text-[10px] font-semibold text-slate-800 truncate">Lucas T.</p>
                      </div>
                      <p class="text-[9px] text-amber-700 font-bold truncate">R$ 850</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Coluna 3: Ganho (drop zone destacado) -->
                <div class="bg-emerald-50 rounded-lg border-2 border-dashed border-emerald-300 p-2.5 relative">
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2.5">
                    <p class="text-[11px] font-semibold text-emerald-700 flex items-center gap-1">
                      <span>✨</span> Ganho
                    </p>
                    <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-emerald-700 tabular-nums">R$ 4,2k</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="space-y-1.5">
                    <div class="bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-200 rounded p-2">
                      <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 mb-1">
                        <div class="size-4 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-400 to-indigo-500 text-white text-[8px] font-bold flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">J</div>
                        <p class="text-[10px] font-semibold text-slate-800 truncate">João P.</p>
                      </div>
                      <p class="text-[9px] text-emerald-700 font-bold truncate">R$ 780</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-200 rounded p-2">
                      <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 mb-1">
